Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:35.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs28\shad0}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N军务与理想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:43.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在 西罗·阿玛达少尉的审问会开庭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:50.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,罪嫌是间谍行为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说什么亏心事也没做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:57.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不那样做的话 APSARAS已落入联邦之手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:03.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你今天的打扮十分女性化喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:07.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:10.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是恋爱中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没那种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:28.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了生存下去 才与那个人合作的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:33.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不觉得过于神秘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,以后 一定还能再见面的吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,分成了敌我阵营在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人中还是有好人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可以互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在这愚蠢的战争中...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:59.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一仅有的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉 我只问你一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你还做得到向敌人开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在宣布审问会的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,西罗·阿玛达少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:01.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,目前这段时期对你施行禁闭 等候处分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就此退庭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,呵 真是新手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,以为这样就能掩饰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了取得粮食 对上面的村子采取佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你带新兵从桥的那一头绕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:45.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 亚斯 我们可不是无赖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不用跟我讲大道理了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,总之给我食物吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可以杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一个家伙从密林中接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个是从河里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个从桥的方向过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去向爸爸报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:15.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别摔倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:22.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙的目的真的如她所说就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 万一发现我们是反抗组织的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:48.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,将你的基地作为再整编奥德萨势力的据点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 别发火嘛 天才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:54.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,战争只不过是攻阵游戏的对打而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:59.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,凭你的一个玩具 想改变大局也未免太儿戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,决战是在宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:06.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在到了就算是多一个兵力也要送上宇宙去的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:12.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为此要利用你那里作为动力是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧 基尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS的开发要终止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:27.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是身为吉翁要遵循的“义”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,战争贩子 也想来跟我谈“义”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,原子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,米诺夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,向来都是科学家将战争的局面改变了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:54.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你进入田地的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,先开口的人就算输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:51.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我那女儿呀 即使面对MS还是那么强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:55.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,作为我的接班人实在让我非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:08:00.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 她好像与那个联邦士官有点纠缠不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 多少有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是情窦初开了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:10.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对那个家伙呀 不懂情趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,东面又来了两台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 全都躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他们察觉这里是据点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:34.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对付这种村子有什么好啰唆的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮个忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,亚斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是故意要引起麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:04.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只不过是想跟你们分一些粮食而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那就至少别把这么危险的东西开过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就讲清楚的话 不就没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被人追赶着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都只好慎重而行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里没什么好东西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:21.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的可是MS 没必要对她示弱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(这场雨下得真大)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 把伏特加整瓶拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不要加冰块 太冷了 吃不消啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长居然是吉翁的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:41.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,08小队真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:46.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长他 才不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:51.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 托他的福 你们没有任务才能大白天就泡在酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒也没有什么好抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,唉哟哟 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:04.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,当做交换条件 告诉你们一个有趣的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:07.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个缠着你们的游击队女孩的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:09.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被吉翁袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪的村子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那 战斗呢 琪琪没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情形就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:21.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是用地下声纳 知道他们在那里罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:22.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不确认清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经做了报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,必要的话 自然会接到出击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:33.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你们以外的小队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你们提供贵重的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:42.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了道谢 我请你喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我去通知队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,(这个混蛋)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:49.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小子 忘记拿信了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:53.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小岛大队长那边好像没有出击的意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说保护游击队 不在任务范围之内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:03.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,让禁闭中的你得知这个消息似乎太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,总比不知道的好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:10.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吧 这可是会上军法会议的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,军 军法会议...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:16.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 应该不会判死刑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不会抛弃同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:23.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,送上美味的三明治来慰劳我们的恩情 不还可是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是这样 我还是想去救琪琪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:29.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我以小队长的身份下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,08小队 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太轻率了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:41.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们3个因接受队长命令而行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一切责任就得由这傻小子担上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而这个就可以派上用场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:50.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,命令书？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还有大队长的签名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我会算你们便宜一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:02.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,人生不能总是正面突破的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:08.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候也必需迎合世俗的观点来做事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还不想那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是傻小子的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,把帐记上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,欠的钱一定会还的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:27.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你当不成好军人的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:56.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么明明是对MS战 却要我们在这么远的地方待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:57.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长一定有他自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大概想显示一下自己的身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 山达斯 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:17.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,收到我的信号后就射击敌人的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 那我就移动到射程之内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就从那里射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:25.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:29.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里离那村子有将近8000米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对手可是有核融合炉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要是瞄准偏差了2米的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:40.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人进入到村子内的话就没办法用MS进攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,米凯尔 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:49.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请至少让我们再接近2000米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:54.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,07小队是在那里探测到ZAKU的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是以敌人的规格...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,村民现在就像是被当作人质一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不能由我们这边挑起战端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:11.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,核融合炉爆炸的话 敌我都会全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,最坏情况下我会使1台无法活动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,其余两台就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,用那种反战车炮...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:29.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,机师有属于机师自己的作战方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:31.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了我大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:36.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,米凯尔你在这里确保了通信之后 到汽垫车上待命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,关于审问会的事情 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能自杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要像以前那样下命令说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,“全员 要活着回来”...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 我什么也不动就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:03.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是吉翁的弹壳吗 能给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:07.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是送来好吃的饭的回礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:15.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,脑子坏了吗 跟小孩子打交道一点意思都没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点嫩 可也不能太挑剔了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,亚斯 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我会上报你是战死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 放开她就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:51.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过得先把饭留下来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:57.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不可为了报复 让村子变成战场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要等待时机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最大倍率了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:34.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:37.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快动手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样就不能让他们活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙是游击队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:50.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到不得了的地方来征粮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:53.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔 此地不宜久留 快逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是 亚斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉他吧 我来掩护 你能够跳跃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 只是一次的话应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:05.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 不想放人逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:33.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,西罗 你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:40.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险 可以动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:46.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你 在保护我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为你做这些作为报答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有1台被... 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:25.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不让我们走的话 村子很快会成为战场的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不让你活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,女人和小孩赶快逃离村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:33.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能够战斗的人就把他们逼到河边去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,河边？难道你想让他们逃跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话 村子会完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能报仇 怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也只是在拼命求生存而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:48.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个联邦的傻小子又懂什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要杀光他们才能泄我们的恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪你也是同样的想法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:59.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 要替爸爸报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是天真的理想论吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:11.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此 我还是想救ZAKU的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙在胡说八道什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,西罗...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,光束步枪预备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,光束吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:21.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 朝左偏移0.2度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再做无意义的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:42.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧 可救你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:46.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,连德尔也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:49.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真是自大的游击队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:06.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对人兵器！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:43.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:48.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你还做得到向敌人开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:04.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:07.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,也没能拯救村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:11.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就连自己的话也没有办法证明...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:17.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:21.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你没来的话 我们可能全都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:22.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琪琪...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:24.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在再对我这么温柔的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:30.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.60,0:24:19.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚康复后回到了08小队
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.28,0:24:22.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们接到的新命令是对敌方阵地实行迂回进攻的空投作战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.89,0:24:25.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,首次参加空投战不知所措的卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.29,0:24:27.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉有些不对劲的山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.88,0:24:29.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:32.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,仍处于迷惘之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.74,0:24:36.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 无论如何 小队都必须得重拾自我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:40.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 机动战士GUNDAM第08MS小队
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:42.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:11.40,Notes,NTP,0,0,0,,（ＭＳ- ０５Ｂ［ＺＡＫＵＩ］：通称旧扎古吉翁公国军开发的史上第１种量产型机动战士其采用的旧制式动力核心\N的输出功率低下在一年战争爆发前夕已基本为ＭＳ- ０６所替代仅有少数被投入到战争初期的奇袭战中）　　　　　\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:55.54,Notes,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnSimHei\fs14}[由于奥德萨被攻陷 吉翁公国军在欧洲战线上的残余部队向宇宙方面和向东方全面撤军  这个以队长托宝的名字来命名的小队便是从奥德萨一路撤退至远东战线来的]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:35.54,Notes,NTP,0,0,0,,(与联邦军的编制不同 吉翁公国军的机动战士小队仅由3台MS组成 没有任何支援作战用及提供补给的车辆 作战补给完全依赖作战基地和沿战线架起的小型补给站 因而小队的作战半径范围非常地小)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:41.44,Notes,NTP,0,0,0,,(注意头上的角 这是吉翁公国军给予扎古系列MS小队队长机的标识  同时也是MS专用的广域天线 因此在吉翁的MS小队里 队长机除负责指挥行动外 还兼负责通讯和临场侦察的任务)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.14,Notes,NTP,0,0,0,,(吉翁公国军机动战士用175毫米口径无后坐力反MS炮)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:11.40,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,嵐の中で輝いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:15.40,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,その夢をあきらめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.15,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,傷ついたあなたの背中の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:22.60,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,天使の羽そっと抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:27.20,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱いてあげたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:38.95,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼く果てない宇宙の片隅で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:45.52,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,生まれた夢が今小さくても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:53.72,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,凍りつくような強い風でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:01:02.60,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,その胸に輝く夢を消したり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:06.22,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そうよ消したりなんか出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:09.62,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,嵐の中で輝いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:13.62,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,その夢をあきらめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.37,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,傷ついたあなたの背中の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:21.12,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,天使の羽そっと抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:25.42,Jp-OP,NTP,0,0,0,,抱いてあげたい
